The Riot Family consists of several sub-projects. These are:

 * riot - A data management frontend
 * forms - A library to build dynamic HTML forms
 * common - A collection classes shared by several sub-projects
 * cachius - A caching library for the Spring MVC framework
 * pages - CMS features for websites
 * riot-hibernate - Hibernate 3 integration
 
The 'jslibs' directory contains 3rd party JavaScript libraries and some Ant
files to package them as JARs.
